description: First published in 1975, the Oblique Strategies are a collection of brief aphorisms meant to stimulate creativity. Such as “Give way to your worst impulse,” “Question the heroic approach,” and “Work at a different speed.”
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Oblique Strategies for a strategy
Alexa ask Oblique Strategies for a different approach
Alexa ask Oblique Strategies for inspiration
name: Oblique Strategies
shortDescription: Ask Alexa for an oblique strategy to help you solve a problem.
